snippet.title: Owlboy Demo Launch Trailer(Official)
snippet.description:
The official Owlboy Demo launch trailer. 

NOTICE: This is a outdated version of Owlboy, new gameplay footage will be released soon.

Demo is also out of date, and has been removed from our website, but can still be found on FilePlanet(Windows, .exe).

http://www.fileplanet.com/221992/220000/fileinfo/Owlboy-Demo

Website: http://www.dpadstudio.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/pages/D-Pad-Studio/155217651187273
Twitter: http://twitter.com/#!/DPadStudio

Music & Direction: Jonathan Geer
D-Pad Studio
